OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,FA 160-year-old private school in
OL,7,FOxfordshire has announced it is
OL,8,Fclosing with immediate effect.
OL,10,FGovernors at Our Lady's Abingdon (OLA)
OL,11,Fsay extensive talks took place with
OL,12,Fother schools and organisations, with
OL,13,Fthe hope of securing a merger or
OL,14,Facquisition but talks broke down.
OL,16,FThe school says it has been under
OL,17,Feconomic pressure citing the
OL,18,Fintroduction of VAT on school fees,
OL,19,Fand rising operational costs as two of
OL,20,Fthe reasons.
