OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the school said its
OL,7,Fimmediate focus will be on supporting
OL,8,Ffamilies in securing alternative
OL,9,Fschool places, assisting staff through
OL,10,Fthe redundancy process, and helping
OL,11,Fthem find new employment.
OL,13,FA statement read: "It is with our
OL,14,Fdeepest regret that we inform our
OL,15,Fparents, students, staff, and local
OL,16,Fcommunity that the Governors have
OL,17,Ftaken the heartbreaking decision to
OL,18,Fclose the school with immediate effect.
