OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,F"This course of action has been taken
OL,7,Fonly after exhausting every possible
OL,8,Foption to secure the schools' future.
OL,9,FFor more than 160 years, OLA has
OL,10,Fdelivered a distinctive education
OL,11,Frooted in Catholic values, guiding
OL,12,Fgenerations of young people to fulfil
OL,13,Ftheir potential.
OL,15,F"The schools' proud legacy has been
OL,16,Fbuilt on academic ambition,
OL,17,Fexceptional pastoral care, and the
OL,18,Funwavering dedication of its staff,
OL,19,Fpast and present.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
