OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,F"In recent months, the Governors have
OL,7,Fexplored every possible avenue to
OL,8,Favoid closure. Extensive talks took
OL,9,Fplace with other schools and
OL,10,Forganisations, with the hope of
OL,11,Fsecuring a merger or acquisition.
OL,13,F"Until very recently, there was
OL,14,Fgenuine optimism that a solution could
OL,15,Fbe found. Sadly, those talks broke
OL,16,Fdown last week, leaving no viable path
OL,17,Fforward.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
