PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1754930172
OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,F"A range of economic pressures has led
OL,7,Fto this outcome, mainly the
OL,8,Fintroduction of VAT on school fees,
OL,9,Fhigher National Insurance
OL,10,Fcontributions, the ending of business
OL,11,Frates relief for independent schools,
OL,12,Fand rising operational costs.
OL,14,F"Despite every effort to limit fee
OL,15,Fincreases, affordability has become a
OL,16,Fgrowing concern for an increasing
OL,17,Fnumber of families. This has led to a
OL,18,Fsharp decline in pupil numbers in
OL,19,Frecent months, threatening the
OL,20,Fschool's short and long-term viability.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
