OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1754930172
OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,F"The closure will affect the entire
OL,7,Fschool community and beyond the wider
OL,8,FAbingdon area. Our immediate focus
OL,9,Fwill be on supporting families in
OL,10,Fsecuring alternative school places in
OL,11,FOxfordshire, assisting staff through
OL,12,Fthe redundancy process, and helping
OL,13,Fthem find new employment.
OL,15,F"A contingency plan is in place to
OL,16,Fensure Year 11 and Year 13 students
OL,17,Freceive full support with their
OL,18,Fexamination results and onward
OL,19,Fprogression.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
