OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1754930172
OL,3,COxfordshire private school announces
OL,4,Cclosure after 160 years
OL,6,F'We are truly heartbroken to have
OL,7,Ftaken the decision to close OLA. Our
OL,8,Fdeepest gratitude goes to the
OL,9,Fremarkable staff, loyal parents, and
OL,10,Finspiring students who have made OLA
OL,11,Fsuch a special place for so many years.
OL,13,F"The spirit of this community, and the
OL,14,Fvalues it upholds, will endure long
OL,15,Fafter our doors close."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
